name: Google Developer Day India Extended ‘17 Ouargla
description:
GDG community! We’re back!
With a new exciting event the “Google developer days India 17 extended, Ouargla”, GDD India,
on the 18th and 19th of February, in the scientific cultural center.
GDG Ouargla with the collaboration of both GDG Constantine and Zoom club without failing to mention Sada youth would gladly invite you guys to enjoy our awesome events once again!
This time with more conferences and workshops in varied fields plus the talks from the GDD India 17,
the surprises are just getting started stay tuned.

La communauté de GDG Ouargla !
Nous sommes de retour !
Avec un autre événement éblouissant : "Google Developper Day India 17 extended, Ouargla" L'événement aura lieu le 18 et le 19 février dans le centre culturel scientifique. GDG Ouargla avec la collaboration de GDG Constantine et Zoom Club sans oublier Sada Youth vous invitent à nous rejoindre encore une fois à nos événements, et cette fois ci y aura plus de conférences et plus de workshops en plusieurs domaines différents, ainsi que des discussions de GDD india 17. Et y aura plus de surprises dans les prochains jours, alors restez à l'écoute

name: Flutter Study Jam

venue.name: ODEJ ouargla
venue.address_1: cité sidi Abdelkader en face hopital de maternité ouargla 30000

description:
Flutter is Google’s mobile app SDK for crafting high-quality native interfaces on iOS and Android in record time. Flutter works with existing code, is used by developers and organizations around the world, and is free and open source.
By the end of this Study Jam, you should have all the tools you need to be able to jump in and create mobile apps from scratch using the Flutter framework.
You will need to bring your own computer with you
